        "story_body": "<p>Happie started with a simple belief: what you drink should make you feel good — and you should feel good about drinking it.</p><p>Founded in 2019 by Pete Olander, Happie is a functional beverage company rooted in Northern California’s plant medicine culture. We make two product lines — hemp-derived Delta-9 THC seltzers and Fungi Fusion adaptogenic mushroom drinks — designed for adults who want something better than alcohol and more effective than another sparkling water.</p><p>Every can is batch-tested, transparently labeled, and formulated with intention. Our THC seltzers use nano-emulsified hemp extract for fast-acting effects you can feel in 15 minutes — not two hours. Our Fungi Fusion line delivers clinical-dose functional mushrooms (Lion’s Mane, Cordyceps, and Reishi) with ocean-derived minerals, no THC, and no compromises.</p><p>We’re not here to follow the beverage industry playbook. We’re here to rewrite it — with science-backed formulations, radical transparency, and a brand built on the belief that wellness and enjoyment belong in the same can.</p>",
